				\begin{document}$$\hat \pi \, > \, 0.2$$\end{document}π^>0.2, based on which we removed one member of each relative pair. PCA estimated 20 PCs which were used in empirical evaluation of covariates to be included in association analyses. Furthermore, for quality control purpose, we performed PCA of our data together with 1000 Genomes Project data on HapMap individuals and SweGen data on NSPHS individuals. The same quality steps were followed for the identification of eligible SNPs in the combined data.
